captions.text: - Well, hello everyone!
My name is Tyler Oakley, and today
it's like a rainy day in L.A.
and I'm just chillin' inside,
hanging out in some pajamas.
I'm wearing this shirt that I made
when I tie-dyed with Hannah Hart

and it's comfortable, and I
was just looking over here
and I have a whole stack of stuff
that you guys have sent me,

and I was like, you know
what, I feel like just
opening up some P.O. Box stuff, because
whenever I'm in like a gloomy mood,

y'all always cheer me up with
the things that you send me

so without further ado, it
is time to open some shit
y'all sent to my P.O. Box.
We have, oh my (laughs)
Wait, okay, so I did a little
how I get ready in the morning video
and I told you guys that with my hair,
if I get it wet, the more it's like wet
and shampooed and stuff like that,
the more the color comes out quicker

so I was telling you guys about
how I have to wear sometimes
a shower cap and I feel ridiculous

and somebody has sent
me a frog shower cap!
Oh my god!
And Izzie, who sent this, says

"Hi, my name is Izzie and I'm
a 13 year old British girl,

"and I have been watching
your videos for two years
"and I absolutely love you.
"I was shopping and I saw this,
"and instead of your pink one,
"you can now wear this frog one."
I am so excited for this!
This might be my favorite new thing ever.
Thank you so much, Izzie.
You are my favorite.
Oh my god, somebody sent me
an electronic yodeling pickle.
(yodeling music)
Are you done? (laughs)

Things that I don't
- (yodeling music)

- Listen, things that I
don't think I need in my life
a yodeling pickle, but now that I have it,
I'm like wow, how did I live without this?
Thank you.

Okay, so the next package,
obviously I know what it is.
It's my NatureBox delivery.
As you guys know, I recommend a new snack
on NatureBox every single month,
and this month, I am recommending

the Kung Pao Pretzels,
if you like a little kick
to your favorite little snack,
these are amazing
and usually I don't like spicy things
but these are so delicious
so if you want them,

all you've got to do is go to
NatureBox dot com slash Tyler.

You go online, you pick
what snacks you want,
they send them to your front door,
you do not have to go to a store.
They come every single month,
and you can get like a big box,

you can get a small
box, whatever you want.

The food is so good and
delicious and healthy

and like low in trans fats
and also, like, actually good

and as you guys know, I
don't talk about something

so again, NatureBox dot com slash Tyler.
If you use that link, you will get
a whole bunch of snacks for free.
You are welcome in advance.
Okay, so this is from Pennsylvania.
Let's see what we got.
Oh my gosh, wait, I am going to love this

and I already know I
am going to love this.

Why are you guys sending
me such cute things?
Sometimes y'all send me, like, fun things

but sometimes y'all send
me like cute things.
Look at this short sleeve button down.
Lord knows I will wear this!
I am so in love with this!
Is there a note in here?
I need to give you some love, let's see.

Oh my gosh, it's a
penguin, speaking Hebrew!

I can't read Hebrew anymore,
it's been some years.

Happy Hanukkah, Tyler!
I've been a fan of yours

since way back in the day
when you were in college

and I have been so pleased
with your recent success.
Thank you!
Thank you for all your years of smiles,
and have a great holiday season.
This is so cute, I am going to be
wearing this in an upcoming video.
Thank you, Sarah, Happy Hanukkah.

Dear Tyler, hello from
Tumblr headquarters.

Thank you so much for
using Tumblr as a platform
to share your creativity with the world.

You are seriously so
insanely awesome, awww.

Here is a little gift to
show our appreciation.
From Tumblr, thank you Tumblr!
We've got, like a little Tumblr tote,

a Tumblr tank top, a Tumblr
t-shirt I am obsessed with this.
Another tank top to match my hair.

A Tumblr hat, and this
one might be my favorite.
It's another Tumblr shirt, and it's like
black on black on black on black,
and you know that I love black on black.

Thank you so much, Tumblr,
for all the fun gifts,

but lord knows I don't
need all these things!
Plus, I want to spread the love, so

if you would like to
win one of these things,

all you've got to do
is follow me on Tumblr.

and leave the link to your
Tumblr in the comments below

and let me know what you
post about on Tumblr.

I'm going to be picking
a whole bunch of people
to win some fun prizes.
Thank you Tumblr!

Okay, so this is from
Katherine in Chicago, Illinois.
Let's see what she sent me.

Okay, so this looks like
it's in another language.
What do we have?
No!!! (Laughs)
Wait, oh my god, I am obsessed with you!

not really back in the day

maybe a month ago, I did

that I was obsessed with
and everyone was like

why are you talking about

and including markers?

Illinois, has sent me
every color of this marker!
I am obsessed!

I will now be signing
some of your posters.

If you buy a poster, I am
going to be signing some

in some colorful colors,
thanks to Katherine.

Thank you, Katherine,
you are so thoughtful!
Okay, so the next piece of mail I have

is from Ben in Anaheim, and
it's a cute little envelope
that's like rainbow colored and it says
Do not open until you do a P.O. Box video,

so I'm like okay, Ben,
your wish is my command.

Okay, so Ben sent me a
letter, and it's his story,
and it's all about how he finds strength
in a lot of his favorite YouTubers
and his favorite celebrities.
Thank you, Ben, for sharing your story.

He, of course, includes his
Twitter and his Instagram

because shameless self promotion
at its best, I approve.
Don't feel bad, your drawing is incredible

and still, somehow better
than anything I could ever do.
Okay, so the last thing I'm going to open,
I think I know what it is,
but this was sent to my P.O. Box,

and this is like the
heaviest thing in the world.

Umm, but it's humongous, I
don't know if you can tell

but this is like the heaviest
thing in the world, so

I am going to open it, oh my
god, oh my goodness gracious.
Okay, wait, so there is a letter attached.
It says "Dear Tyler Oakley,
"You delivered the audience,
"now we're delivering the rewards.

"At YouTube--" I knew
it was going to be this.
"At YouTube, you set the gold standard
"by surpassing one million subscribers,
"so please accept with our congratulations

"this gold play button to
commemorate your achievement."

If you recall, I reached a
million subscribers last summer

and it took them a while,
I think, to send it to me
but you know what, better late than never.
I think it's just in time,

because I just hit six
million subscribers!

So thank you to everyone
who has subscribed so far,

even though they may be five
million subscribers behind,

it is still an amazing
gift, and it still means

so much to me that you
guys have subscribed.

You've watched my videos,
you enjoy my stuff.

Honestly, this might be the
coolest thing in the world
but it is also the heaviest.
But that is all I have for you guys today.
I hope you have a fabulous life.

Thank you for putting me
in such a better mood.

I know it's gloomy out,
but your guys's gifts
make me so happy, so thank you.
If you like this video and you want me
to do more P.O. Box videos in the future,
just give this video a thumbs up.

Let's see if we can get 100,000
thumbs up in the first day.

I mean now that I have a
million subscribers plaque,
I feel like we should ask for a million,
but I'm just going to say,

let's see if we can get
100,000 in the first day.

I'm watching you push
the thumbs up button.
Bam, you did it.

If you want to see my latest
video, click right there.
It's really fun, enjoy it.

If you want to hear the latest
podcast, click right there.
It is all about Christmas,
and the festivities of the holidays.

If you would like to be
my person of the week,
click right there, get something from
District Lines dot com slash Tyler Oakley.
With all of your new holiday gift money,

I think right now is the perfect
time to get something cute.

But yes, that is all I
have for you guys today.
I hope you have a fabulous life
and I will see you guys next time.
Later!

(yodeling music)
- Are you done yet?

I don't know what's
happening to my channel.
I'm sorry. (laughs)
